 Apple’s Center Stage feature. It’ll run most apps with ease, but you’ll probably want something more if you’re hoping to use it as a portable workstation or video editing machine.</li></ul></div><div class="duet--article--article-body-component"><div class="duet--article--product-card clear-both my-40 flex flex-col border-t border-franklin pt-20 sm:flex-row"><a class="relative block aspect-square h-min w-full sm:float-left sm:mb-20 sm:mr-20 sm:w-[300px] sm:min-w-[300px]" data-item-id="Np6F6F" href="https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MU8F2AM-A-Pencil-Generation/dp/B07K1WWBJK?tag=theverge02-20" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><span style="box-sizing:border-box;display:block;overflow:hidden;width:initial;height:initial;background:none;opacity:1;border:0;margin:0;padding:0;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0"><img alt="A photo of Apple’s second-gen Apple Pencil being used on an iPad Pro." src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover"/><noscript><img alt="A photo of Apple’s second-gen Apple Pencil being used on an iPad Pro." loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;right:0;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0;border:none;margin:auto;display:block;width:0;height:0;min-width:100%;max-width:100%;min-height:100%;max-height:100%;object-fit:cover" sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 300px" srcSet="https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/376x376/filters:focal(1020x680:1021x681):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/13385143/akrales_181101_3064_0171.jpg 376w, https://duet-cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0x0:2040x1360/384x384/filters:focal(1020x680:1021x681):format(webp)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chor